inline int read()//快读 
{
    int x = 0 ,y = 1;
    char c = getchar();
    while(c > '9' || c < '0')
    {
        if(c == '-')y = -1;
        c = getchar();
    }
    while(c <= '9' && c >= '0')
    {
        x = x * 10 + c - '0';
        c = getchar();
    }
    return x * y;
}

int main()
{
	n = read(); k = read();//输入
	if(n % 2 == 0)//特判
	{
		cout << 0;
		return 0;
	}
	cout << p[n][k];//输出
	return 0;//好习惯
}
